- [sighs] Man, I wish Big Booty
Judy was blowing me up,

02:34.538 --> 02:36.638
but, no, it's the school's
basketball coach.

02:36.774 --> 02:38.407
- What did the coach
want?

02:38.542 --> 02:40.576
