because I won a championship.

02:58.896 --> 03:00.963
- You were 11.

03:01.098 --> 03:02.564
- And? What that mean?

03:02.700 --> 03:04.433
Shoot, the team--the other
team we played against, ssh,

03:04.568 --> 03:06.034
