alright?

03:10.174 --> 03:11.273
Now, come on, chop-chop.

03:11.408 --> 03:13.508
What you waiting for?
Let's go.

03:13.644 --> 03:15.510
- My waffles to come
out the toaster.

03:15.646 --> 03:16.545
- Man, forget them
waffles.

03:16.680 --> 03:17.880
You got tryouts today,

03:18.015 --> 03:19.281
