you trying to teach him.

05:09.460 --> 05:10.926
- What he's saying is,
he coached me on how

05:11.061 --> 05:13.795
to dribble, pass, and shoot.

05:13.931 --> 05:15.130
- You're not teaching him

05:15.265 --> 05:17.099
