of the game!

05:19.269 --> 05:22.137
- And what's that?
- Trash talking.

05:22.272 --> 05:24.740
I mean, how to get up in
a player's head, man.

05:24.875 --> 05:26.408
- Trash talking?

05:26.543 --> 05:28.176
- And you gotta hit 'em with
the, "Your grandmamma

05:28.312 --> 05:33.115
