gonna do?'

05:42.760 --> 05:43.792
- Well, guess what?

05:43.927 --> 05:45.961
My grandmother
was your wife.

05:46.096 --> 05:47.262
- Mm.

05:47.398 --> 05:49.031
Stay out of my head, boy.

05:49.166 --> 05:50.465
- Okay, first lesson,

05:50.601 --> 05:52.534
forget everything
Grandpa just said, alright?

05:52.669 --> 05:53.535
