I wore in my movie

06:00.577 --> 06:04.279
"Disco Kung-Fu Cheerleaders

06:04.415 --> 06:08.350
Funk Up Detroit."

06:08.485 --> 06:10.085
- Think I've seen that.
- And I heard that there

06:10.220 --> 06:12.487
was a budding basketball
star out here,

06:12.623 --> 06:16.324
and I wanted to come
and cheer you on to victory.

06:16.460 --> 06:18.627
- Okay, well, let's see
what you got.

06:18.762 --> 06:21.363
- Well, that's why
I wore this,

06:21.498 --> 06:24.599
darling.
- Eh.

06:24.735 --> 06:26.334
I meant show us a cheer.

06:26.470 --> 06:29.271
- Oh, right.
Okay.

06:31.642 --> 06:35.777
Don't score me any weed,
or LSD,

06:35.913 --> 06:39.781
just score a basket
for me, yeah!

06:39.917 --> 06:42.784
Go! Team! Whoo!

06:45.689 --> 06:47.656
- Really, Miss Anastasia?

06:47.791 --> 06:49.224
- What?

06:49.359 --> 06:53.095
I haven't cheered
since the '70s.

06:53.230 --> 06:54.296
My back.

06:57.768 --> 07:01.136
- Well, this was
really fun, Dad.

07:01.271 --> 07:03.505
- Yeah, yeah, you just remember
this when you go

07:03.640 --> 07:07.275
to the NBA.
[laughs]

07:07.411 --> 07:09.778
I had fun, too, Son.
- [horn honking]

07:09.913 --> 07:11.780
- Oh, there's your ride.

07:11.915 --> 07:13.615
- Oh, I thought you
were taking me.

07:13.750 --> 07:16.084
- Nah, man, I got a lot of stuff
to do around here, just took

07:16.220 --> 07:17.953
a couple minutes so I could get
my son in shape, you know?

07:18.088 --> 07:19.387
But your homie Peanut,

07:19.523 --> 07:20.722
his father
gonna give you a ride.

07:20.858 --> 07:24.126
Yeah, that's my boy!
Yeah!

07:24.261 --> 07:25.393
NBA!

07:25.529 --> 07:29.664
