give advice in three areas:

07:39.042 --> 07:40.909
fame, romance,

07:41.044 --> 07:42.878
and what to look for in a good
attorney.

07:43.013 --> 07:45.580
Divorce attorney,
that is.

07:45.716 --> 07:49.117
- Right. I need to know how to
set a romantic scene.

07:49.253 --> 07:51.520
- I'm wondering, is this
not something you should

07:51.655 --> 07:52.854
ask your mother?

07:52.990 --> 07:54.556
- Oh, I'd rather
talk to you.

07:54.691 --> 07:55.957
You know, you just seem
like you've been around.

07:56.093 --> 07:57.292
- BOTH: [laughing]

07:57.427 --> 07:59.828
- I'm not sure whether to
be offended

07:59.963 --> 08:02.364
or to pat myself on the back.

08:02.499 --> 08:04.199
- Oh, no, no, I don't
mean like you're a thot

08:04.334 --> 08:06.301
or anything, you know,
you're just so classy

08:06.436 --> 08:08.103
and experienced with
fancy things.

08:08.238 --> 08:10.405
I mean, you're obviously
the most qualified person here.

08:10.541 --> 08:13.141
- I can't disagree with you
there.

08:13.277 --> 08:16.545
So you wanna set up
a romantic mood?

08:16.680 --> 08:17.779
- Mm-hmm.

08:17.915 --> 08:19.414
- Who's the lucky fella?
Lindor?

08:19.550 --> 08:21.216
- Oh, I'd rather not say.

08:21.351 --> 08:25.120
- Ooh, is it a spy?
An international spy?

08:25.255 --> 08:27.489
That if you told someone
the Soviet Union would

08:27.624 --> 08:31.560
terminate him?
- What's the Soviet Union?

08:31.695 --> 08:34.429
- Whoever it is,

08:34.565 --> 08:37.766
candlelight is key,
the more the better.

08:37.901 --> 08:40.869
The soft light will hide
your crowfeet.

08:41.004 --> 08:42.871
- Ew. I don't have
crow's feet.

08:43.006 --> 08:45.106
