the roses,

08:47.244 --> 08:49.945
however many you can
afford.

08:50.080 --> 08:52.347
White if the relationship
is new.

08:52.482 --> 08:54.516
Yellow if you're gonna
be friends.

08:54.651 --> 08:57.953
And red if you're
ready for the hubba-bubba.

08:58.088 --> 08:59.988
- And what is
hubba-bubba?

09:00.123 --> 09:02.424
- For you, darling,
it's holding hands.

09:02.559 --> 09:05.026
- Oh, okay, red roses,
then definitely red.

09:05.162 --> 09:08.463
- Mood music and
dessert are also a must,

09:08.599 --> 09:11.099
