if I should.

09:29.019 --> 09:31.987
- I just don't want them asking
a hundred million questions.

09:32.122 --> 09:33.455
You know, I was just curious
about how to set

09:33.590 --> 09:36.825
a romantic scene
for the far future.

09:36.960 --> 09:38.059
- The future?

09:38.195 --> 09:41.096
