out there lying

16:42.819 --> 16:44.752
to their father, got me
up at the school looking

16:44.888 --> 16:48.923
like boo-boo the fool.
- Jeremy, calm down.

16:49.059 --> 16:50.525
- You know what?

16:50.660 --> 16:51.693
I can't believe you,
man.

16:51.828 --> 16:53.261
Just go to your room.

16:53.396 --> 16:55.263
- But, Dad--
- Go!

17:01.738 --> 17:03.771
- What are we gonna do
about this kid lying--

17:03.907 --> 17:07.442
- I hate to intrude,
