after everyone goes to sleep.

17:15.919 --> 17:17.251
- With who?

17:17.387 --> 17:22.190
- Lindor.
- [sighs]

17:22.325 --> 17:25.393
- Sandra!
- Shh! Jeremy. Jeremy.

17:25.528 --> 17:26.928
Let me handle this,
baby, this needs to be

17:27.063 --> 17:28.296
a mother-daughter conversation.

17:28.431 --> 17:30.298
- Why? She went behind
my back too.

17:30.433 --> 17:33.034
- Uh, just let me
handle it.

17:33.169 --> 17:35.136
- Alright, but if I catch
Lindor

17:35.271 --> 17:36.471
trying to sneak up in
here again--

17:36.606 --> 17:38.406
- Mm-hmm.
- --it's gonna be a 10-13.

17:38.541 --> 17:41.109
- Okay.
- A 10-14, and a 10-15.

17:41.244 --> 17:43.678
- Um--
