- Oh, you know?

18:02.332 --> 18:04.866
- Why you keep
checking your phone?

18:05.001 --> 18:07.201
- Because I'm a teenager.

18:07.337 --> 18:08.469
- Keep getting smart
with me.

18:08.605 --> 18:10.271
I know what you're up to,
